oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: School Time - Wheels Of Progress - 1947-02-03 - Part 4
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 4 of the first episode of the new School Time series 'Wheels of Progress', originally broadcast on WLS, Chicago, IL, February 3, 1947 at 1:15pm. Presented by Josephine Wetzler.
